S       ← 5
S′      ← ↯S_S
NumQ    ← 4
RCDLDR  ← ⊚/↥⊟₄⊃(=S′⇡⊙⊣|=⍉S′⇡⊙⊢|=˙⊞+⇡⊙/+|=˙⊞-⇡⊙/-)
Posns   ← ⊙◌♭₂°⊡°△S_S
PeerMap ← map⟜≡(□RCDLDR S) Posns
Peers   ← ˜get PeerMap
Free    ← ⊚=0°⊚∧(⊂°□Peers)⊙[]
⧅> NumQ Posns            # All possible white(1) queen positions.
▽≥4≡◇⧻⊸≡(□Free)          # Check all peers of each, see if 4 spaces are left.
⊸⧻⬚0≡(⬚0↥⊃(×2°⊚Free|°⊚)) # Put black(2) queens in *all* of those.
